reviewText:
3 of our favorite movies in one package!!!  Makes us laugh like "thooo utes" every single time we watch them!!
I thought they would all be on one disk but each movie is a separate disk!  Awesome!
This was perfect. my mom needed a comedy/relaxation gift for her secret Santa at work. It was a great value and came on time! these movies are classics. I definitely recommend this item!
Four separate DVD's, packaged nicely in one case.  Wasn't crazy over Super Troopers movie, but the others are great!
Great quality case and DVD thank you!
office space is a favorite now,  if you have not watched it "sounds like someone has a case of the Mondays"
very favorable
Excellent experience dealing with this seller! Great quality purchase!
Great deal
Great movies for a great price.
My Cousin Vinny plays perfectly. Haven't watched Mrs. Doubtfire yet.
Just got these in the mail and tried playing two of the four dvds, they do not work! So angry that I spent money on this!!
good movie set
not only did I get the one movie that I wanted, I got 4 funny movies
I only ordered this because it included office space but when I received it and put it in my player office space couldn't play
Gave this for a white elephant gift with popcorn & coca colas
As expected
A gift for my niece, great collection. All on their own DVDs

No matter how many times I see each of these films, I always laugh.  Not every film is that timeless.  Truly fun for the older adults in the family...Doubtfire is for kids but the other three films are too raunchy for youngsters...any adult with a sense of humor will enjoy!
Fun collection of good cult favorites. Great idea, good shipping and experience. Thanks!

3 of the greatest movies of all time and a 4th pretty great one? For that price? Not bad at all. Super Troopers is a little out of place here but still a good pick.
I went on Amazon specifically to order My Cousin Vinny and was very pleasantly surprised to see this bundle with 3 other excellent films included.
awesome price and quality!
Funny.
Purchased these while searching for Mrs. Doubtfire, it was cheaper to buy the combo pack than to purchase that single DVD.  We enjoyed all of the movies. Great price
as expected
As advertised
great product love these movies
This is worth it just for Mrs. Doubtfire and my cousin vinny!
Bought for office space but got the rest at a great price. The other movies are funny as well. For the price I definitely recommend.
Wanted to own the two funniest movies I have ever seen - My Cousin Vinny, and Office Space. And, lo and behold, here they are in one DVD! Must have!
All four of these movies all really good to are better
These are good off center comedies
This was a great collection of my favorites.
Wonderful price for four great movies!!
Nice collection. Reasonable price.
Great combination
Came quick 4 movies in one , I really only wanted my cousin bunny but what the heck you get 4 :)

It was a perfect gift for my son. He wanted a copy of "My Cousin Vinny" and he got the added bonus of 3 additional movies. He was particularly happy to have the Robin Williams classic "Mrs. Doubtfire". It was a big hit.
All of these movies are great! Office Space is the best movie ever created.
Good stuff, I like
